OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775481061
OL,3,CTwo teens arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after boy, 14, shot dead
OL,6,FTwo more teenagers have been arrested
OL,7,Fon suspicion of murder after a 14-year-
OL,8,Fold boy was shot dead in London.
OL,10,FEghosa Ogbebor died in Lord Warwick
OL,11,FStreet, Woolwich, with police called
OL,12,Fto the scene at about 3.40pm on
OL,13,FThursday.
OL,15,FA 16-year-old boy and a 19-year-old
OL,16,Fman have been arrested on Saturday,
OL,17,FMet Police said in its latest update.
OL,18,FThey are currently in custody.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
