PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775481061
OL,3,CTwo teens arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after boy, 14, shot dead
OL,6,FThree other people - two boys aged 14
OL,7,Fand 16 and an 18-year-old man - who
OL,8,Fwere arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,9,Fon Friday have been released on bail.
OL,11,FA 46-year-old man who was arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender
OL,13,Fremains in custody.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Lucie Card
OL,16,Fsaid: "Our team of dedicated
OL,17,Fdetectives are continuing inquiries to
OL,18,Finvestigate Eghosa's tragic death.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
