PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775481061
OL,3,CTwo teens arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after boy, 14, shot dead
OL,6,F"Residents in Woolwich may have
OL,7,Fnoticed a large amount of police
OL,8,Factivity last night, as officers
OL,9,Farrested three further people in
OL,10,Fconnection with the investigation.
OL,12,F"We appreciate the concern that
OL,13,FEghosa's death has caused,
OL,14,Fparticularly among the local community
OL,15,Fwho will continue to see an increased
OL,16,Fpolice presence around the area.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
