FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775481061
OL,3,CTwo teens arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after boy, 14, shot dead
OL,6,F"There may be people who have heard
OL,7,Finformation or witnessed suspicious
OL,8,Factivity in the area but not yet
OL,9,Fcontacted police. We urge these people
OL,10,Fto contact us and assist with the
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,F"We will continue to support and
OL,14,Fupdate Eghosa's family as the
OL,15,Finvestigation continues and our
OL,16,Fthoughts remain with them at this
OL,17,Fincredibly difficult time."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@[O]
